name: Warung Puri Bambu
address: J647+FRC Lapangan umum, Petang, Kec. Petang, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80353, Indonesia
review 1: Very nice place, everything is very clean, the food is great and the people very friendly!!
review 2: I’ve visited this restaurant twice and have been impressed by the peace and solitude it affords when you’ve had enough of the beach club/ Changuu scene.  The food is good, service staff is friendly and helpful, and the owner has plans for a future glamming area.  Check this place out if you want to get off the usual tourist experience!
review 3: Very clean Place, nice Yard, Omelettes are very good, also the Juices.
